metadata.title: TenCloud for Garmin vivoactive HR Smartwatch and Fitbit Surge Superwatch Replacement Band Accessories Silicone Band Holders Keepers Fastener Rings Loops(Black-5 Packs)
features: Compatible with Garmin Vivo active hr Smartwatch/ Fitbit surge super watch. No band, no watch, only replacement pieces.
They will be a perfect replacement for the Fitbit surge/Garmin Vivo active hr Strap fastener
The band connect loops are about 2mm longer than the band. They will fit all size bands of Garmin Vivo active hr and Fitbit surge.
The Vivo active hr/surge band holder has a little extra piece sticking out on the bottom so it "snaps" Into place in the band slots.
If you feel it is too hard to use, you can soak it in Warm/hot water to soften it and slid it onto the band over the buckle.
description: 1. Compatible device: Garmin vivo active HR Fitbit surge super Watch. 2. Width: 30mm /1. 2 in. They will fit all size bands of fitting surge and Garmin vivo active HR Watch3. If you feel it is too hard to use, you can soak it in Warm/hot water to soften it and slid it onto the band over the Buckle4. A good backup if the original sliding band holder broke off your fitting or Garmin Watch5. Package Content: 5 x surge/vivo active HR band holder keeper
